Chiau3 goa2 phah-sng3 chng7 Giau5 Sun3 hit-si5 i2-keng u7 , in-ui7 Su-keng kong2 , Giau5 u7 Bun5-chou2- bio7 , Ge7-chou2 bio7 , iah8 Sun3 u7 khi3 che3 ; taN u7 bio7 tek-khak u7 bok8-chu2 , na7 bo5 , siu7-che3 e5 mih8 chiu7 beh che3 si7-chui7 ? Kiam2- chhai2 u7 lang5 kong2 bo5 tek-khak , in-ui7 cha2 e5 lang5 teh che3 u7 eng7 gin2-a2 chheng7 sian-jin5 e5 i-hok8 choe3 chu2-che3 e5 lang5 ,lang5 che3 i , i3-su3 si7 che3 chou2-kong ; kau3 au7- lai5 e5 lang5 hiam5 chit-ho7 hoat-tou7 m7-ho2 , in-ui7 chiau3 chit-ho7 hoat-tou7 chiu7 pe7 tioh8 pai3 kiaN2 , an2-ni ai3 beh iu2-hau3 tai7-seng biat8 jin5-lun5 , sou2-i2 u7 oaN7 bok8-chu2 ,hoe3 hit- e5 si e5 tai7-chi3 , an2-ni bok8-chu2 si7 khah au7- tai7 e5 lang5 chiah siat ; goa2 kong2 m7-si7 an2- ni , Tiong-kok chheh beng5-beng5 kong2 ¡§ Chu2 sou2-i2 i sin5 , si sou2-i2 siong7-sin5 . ¡¨ ( I3-su3 si7 kong2 , bok8-chu2 si7 beh hou7 sin5 thang i- oa2 , si si7 beh hian2-beng5 sin5 e5 khoan2 . ) An2-ni si kap bok8-chu2 si7 tang5-si5 u7--e5 , chong2-si7 tu2-tu2 tui3 ti7-si5 u7 , goa2 m7-kaN2 toan3 , iau2-ku2 kaN2 kong2 chng7 Giau5-Sun3 e5 si5 i2- keng u7 .
