  Lun7 hit-e5 m7-tioh8 u7 kui2-na7 hang7. 1 . Peh-siN3 lang5 boe7 chhai7--tit . Beh chhai7 sin5-chu2 tek-khak tioh8 u7 thou2-toe7 e5 jin5-kun chiah oe7 choe3-tit, chhin-chhiuN7 Thian-chu2 , Chu-hou5 , kap u7 chhai2-te7 e5 kheng, chi2 kui2 teng2-ho7 e5 lang5 chiah oe7 chhai7--tit . Kiam2-chhai2 u7 lang5 mng7 kong2 . An2-ni chiu7 Tai7-hu , Su7 , i2-kip8 peh-siN3 lang5 beh che3 beh chaiN2-iuN7 ? In3 kong2 , Put-ko3 si7 phou ki2-toh , chhioh8 , lai5 hou7 sin5 oa2 na7- tiaN7 . Sian-jin5 Khong2--si7 , TiN7--si7 , Chhui- si7 , chu3 Le2-ki3 che3-hoat hit-phiN long2-si7 an2-ni kong2; chong2-si7 u7 choe7-choe7 lang5 saN-pok, in-ui7 Le2-ki3 lai7 bo5 beng5-beng5 an2-ni kong2; sui-jian5 an2-ni iau2-ku2 Kong2-iong5 beng5-beng5 kong2 , ¡§ Kheng, Tai7-hu, m7-si7 hit-ho7 u7 thou2-toe7 e5 Jin5-kun boe7 tit- thang khap-hiong2 chiau-bok8 . ¡¨ ( I3-su3 si7 hap8 che3 chou2-kong ) . An2-ni chiu7 beng5-beng5 si7 bo5 sin5-chu2 , in-ui7 na7-bo5 , chiu7 bo5 hun-piat8 chun-kui3 pi-chian7 e5 teng2-te7 . An2-ni chiu7 kin-a2-jit8 lang5-lang5 chhai7 sin5- chu2 , si7 peh-siN3 lang5 chhiam3 eng7 Thian-chu2 , Chu-hou5 e5 le2-sou3 ; che si7 toa7 m7-tioh8 . Siat-su2 lang5 ai3 iu2-hau3 pe7-bu2 , hou7 i chheng7 ng5 leng5-pou5 chheng i choe3 hong5- te3 , an2-ni kiam2-oe7 thang kong2 , Goa2 si7 iu2- hau3 mah ? Cha2 Khong2-chu2 bo5 choe3-koaN bo5 ka-sin5 , tu2-tioh8 piN7 e5 si5 Chu2-Lou7 eng7 lang5 khi2 choe3 i-e5 ka-sin5 , Khong2-chu2 siong7-chhiaN2 tang7-tang7 chek-pi7 i, ho5-hong3 peh-siN3 chhiam3 Thian-chu2 e5 le2 , hit e5 m7-tioh8 kau3 chaiN2-iuN7 ah ? Kiam2- chhai2 u7 lang5 pok kong2, Le2-ki3 sou2-kong2 che3 e5 hoat-tou7 i2-kip8 sin5-chu2 chiah e5 tai7- chi3 , to bo5 kong2 si7 choan chi2 Thian-chu2 , Chu-hou5 , thai2-tho2 oe7 chai m7-si7 chi2 peh- siN3 lang5 ah ? In3 kong2, Le2-ki3 kong2 kau3 che3 , chiu7 soa3 kong2 bio7 , an2-ni thang chai m7- si7 chi2 peh-siN3 lang5 , in-ui7 peh-siN3 lang5 bo5 bio7 , put-ko3 che3 ti7 chhim2-sek na7-tiaN7 . 
  2 . Chiau3 le2-hoat , Thian-chu2 chhit-keng bio7 , hok8-sai7 chhit-tai7 ; Chu-hou5 gou7-keng bio7 , hok8-sai7 gou7-tai7 ; Tai7-hu saN-keng bio7 , hok8-sai7 saN-tai7 ; Tek-su7 nng7-keng bio7 , hok8-sai7 nng7-tai7 ; Koan-su chit8-keng bio7 , hok8-sai7 chit8-tai7, iah8 soa3-chun2 peh-siN3 lang5 che3 chit8-tai7, chong2-si7 boe7 tit thang u7 bio7 . Thian-chu2 , Chu-hou5 , Tai7-hu , in e5 chou2-kong na7 ke3 chhit-tai7 , gou7-tai7 , saN-tai7 , chiu7 bo5 chhai7 ti7 bio7--nih8 , put-ko3 si7 chhai7 ------------------------------------ 
