  ------------------------------------------------------------------------ ti7 toaN5--nih8 , sian7--nih8 ; iah8 bo5 chhin- chhiuN7 ti7 bio7-lai7 e5 si5 , u7 su3-si5 long2 che3 ; kau3 koh-khah ku2 chiu7 tai5 , long2 bo5 koh- chai3 che3 . Koh chit8-keng bio7 chi2 u7 chit8 sian sin5-chu2 ; cha2 Cheng-chu2 mng7 Khong2-chu2 kong2 , ¡§ Bio7--nih8 u7 nng7-sian bok8-chu2 , che si7 tioh8 mah ? ¡¨ Khong2-chu2 kong2 , ¡§ ThiN bo5 nng7 e5 jit8 , kok bo5 nng7 e5 ong5 , bio7 u7 nng7 e5 chu2 , chaiN2-iuN7 si7 le2 goa2 to boe7 hiau2--tit . ¡¨ TaN kin-a2-jit8 peh-siN3 lang5 chhai7 sin5-chu2 m7-na7 si7 che3 chit8-tai7 , saN-tai7 , gou7-tai7 , chhit-tai7 na7-tiaN7 , si7 u7-e5 chhai7 kau3 gou7-lak8 chap8 tai7 e5 sin5-chu2 , iah8 soa3 che3--i ; an2-ni si7 peh-siN3 chhiam3 Thian- chu2 Chu-hou5 e5 le2 , iah8 si7 beh pi2 i koh- khah toa7 ; m7 na7 an2-ni , iah8 si7 chiong kui2-chap8 sin e5 sin5-chu2 chai7 choe3 chit8-keng chit8-te3-toh , che kiam2 m7-si7 ui5-keh8 Khong2- chu2 e5 oe7 , poe7 kou2-cha2 e5 le2-sou3 mah ? 
  3 . Lun7 che3 e5 sou2-chai7 bo5 chiau3 kou2-cha2 e5 hoat-tou7. In-ui7 cha2 e5 hoat-tou7 , peh-siN3 lang5 boe7 tit-thang u7 chou2-bio7 , put-ko3 si7 che3 ti7 chhim2-sek; kin-a2-jit8 e5 lang5 long2 bo5 chiau3 chit-e5 hoat , sou2-u7 e5 sin5-chu2- pang , long2 si7 he7 ti7 thiaN toh teng2 liau2- liau2 ; che kiam2 m7-si7 m7-tioh8 ? U7 lang5 koh-khah toa7 m7-tioh8, chiu7-si7 khi2 su5-tng5 , mng5-bai5-teng2 sia2 ¡§ Bou2-siN3 ka-biau7 ¡¨ . TaN peh-siN3-lang5 to m7-thang u7 bio7 , chaiN2-iuN7 sia2 bio7 ? Siat-su2 sia2 su5-tng5 iah8 si7 m7-tioh8 , in-ui7 peh-siN3 lang5 put-ko3 si7 che3 ti7 chhim2- sek na7-tiaN7 . U7 lang5 koh-khah toa7 m7- tioh8 , chiu7-si7 soa3 che3 ti7 bong7--nih8 ; kiam2- chhai2 u7 lang5 pok-kong2 , Che3-bong7 si7 tui3 cha2 chiu7 u7, thai2-tho2 m7-tioh8 ? Cheng- chu2 kong2 , ¡§ Thai5 gu5 lai5 che3-bong7 m7-tah8- tioh8 than3 pe7-bu2 ti7--teh , eng7 ti , koe , lai5 hok8-sai7 i . ¡¨ Beng7-chu2 kong2 , ¡§ Hit e5 Che5- jin5 khi3 tang-mng5 goa7 chhe7 thiong2-bong7-- nih8 teh che3 e5 lang5. ¡¨ An2-ni che3-bong7 chu7-cha2 chiu7 u7, thai2-tho2 m7-tioh8 ? Goa2 kong2 , M7-si7 an2-ni ; Cheng-chu2 sou2-kong2 e5 che3-bong7 , si7 tu2-a2 khi3 tai5 hit-si5 lai5 che3 , m7-si7 tai5 liau2-au7 siong5-siong5 khi3 che3 ; koh Cheng-chu2 kong2 chit-ku3 si7 in-ui7 khoaN3 lang5 tui3-tiong7 si2-au7 e5 che3 , khah iau3-kin2 siN-cheng5 e5 hok8-sai7 , sou2-i2 kong2 chit-ku3 ; an2-ni Cheng-chu2 sui-bong2 bo5 ka3-lang5 m7-sai2 che3-bong7 , iau2-ku2 beng5- beng5 si7 kong2 che3 bong7 si7 bo5 lou7-eng7 . Lun7-kau3 Beng7-chu2 sou2 kong2--e5 , tioh8 chai he m7-si7 ke2-siat u7 hit-e5 lang5 hit-e5 su7, put-ko3 si7 sit8-sit8 hit-e5 tai7-chi3 lai5 pi2-pok kiu5 hu3-kui3 li7-tat8 e5 lang5 na7-tiaN7; chhin-chhiuN7 i bat chit8-pai2 ka2-siat chit8-e5 Song3- kok e5 lang5 puih8 tiu7-a2 e5 tai7-chi3 lai5 gi7-lun7 khi3 e5 to7-li2 ; sou2-i2 m7-thang phah-sng3 cha2 e5 lang5 sit8-chai7 u7 che3-bong7 . Han3-tiau5 Chhoa3 Iong u7 kong2 , ¡§ Goa2 thiaN-kiN3 cha2 bo5 che3-bong7 e5 tai7-chi3 . ¡¨ Gui7 Bun5-te3 kon