  4 .Goa2 thak8 le2-ki3 che3-gi7 , che3-hoat , che3- thong2 chiah e5 phiN , u7 kong2 ka7 ta-pou- lang5 lip8 sin5-chu2 lai5 che3 , be7-bat thiaN-kiN3 kong2 u7 ka7 hu7-jin5-lang5 lip8 sin5-chu2 lai5 che3 ; sou2-i2 Thian-chu2 , Chu-hou5 , Tai7-hu teng2 , sou2 che3--e5 long2 si7 sian-kun , sian- ong5 , sian-kong , sian-chou2 ; be7-bat thiaN-kiN3 u7 sian thai3-hou7 , sian hu-jin5 , sian chou2- ma2 , sian bu2-chhin . Au7-tai7 e5 lang5 chu7-chok chhong-beng5 , phah-sng3 kong2 cha2 seng3-ong5 seng3-jin5 iau2 bo5 chim-chiok , che3 lam5 bo5 che3 lu2 , sim beh thai2-tho2 oe7 peng5-an ? Tui3 an2-ni lip8 sian-kong e5 bok8- chu2 , iah8 lip8 sian-ma2 e5 bok8-chu2 , phah- sng3 ti3-sek beh ke3-thau5 seng3-jin5 , iu2-hau3 beh ke3-thau5 seng3-jin5 , kong-lo5 beh ke3- thau5 seng3-jin5 . Sit8-chai7 si7 toa7-toa7 put-kham ; siat-su2 si7 chu7-cha2 sou2 siat iah8-si7 u7 chho3 , lan2 Tiong-kok lam5-lu2 hun-piat8 chin-giam5 . Chiau3 le2-ki3 kong2 , Lam5-lu2 m7- thang chham-chham teh-che7, m7-thang tang5 chit8-e5 saN-a2-ke3 , m7-thang tang5 chit8 tiau5 soe2 sin-khu e5 kun, m7-thang saN oa2, m7-thang saN-chioh-mng7; kou chi2-be7 e5 cha-bou2-kiaN2 i2-keng ke3 , to3-lai5 choe3-kheh, hiaN- ti7 m7-thang kap i tang5 toh chiah8 . Sou2 kim3 u7 e5 sui-bong2 si7 siuN-giam5, chong2-si7 u7-e5 tek-khak si7 tioh8 than3, tang5-toh chiah8 na7 thang , tang5-chhng5 khun3 tek-khak si7 boe7 choe3 tit . TaN e5 lang5 lip8 bok8-chu2 , u7-e5 si7 lam5-chu2 , u7 e5 si7 lu2-chu2, chhai7-lai7 choe3 chit8-tui ; phi3-ju7 ta-koaN si2 , chiu7 chhai7 chit8-sin ta-koaN e5 sin5-chu2 ti7 toh-teng2 ; au7- lai5 sim-pu7 si2 , iah8 chhai7 chit8-sin sim-pu7 e5 bok8-chu2 ti7 toh-teng2 ; chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni hap8-le2 mah ? Na7 kong2 bok8-chu2 si7 si2-si2 e5 mih8 boe7 chai , chiu7 mih-sai2 chhai7 , mih- sai2 che3 ? Na7 kong2 si7 u7 chai, chiu7 lam5-lu2 hun7-chhng5, me5-jit8 choe3-tui, hit te3 toh na2 bin5-chhng5, chiu7 lam5-lu2 tang5-chhng5; chin7-chai7 kho2-ouN3, chin7-chai7 kian3-siau3. Choe3 kiaN2-sun e5 lang5 khoan2-thai7 chou2-kon